    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "I have received your letter dated March 13,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "1961, and the interest which prompted your communicating",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "with me is indeed appreciated.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "This Bureau has conducted no investigation of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "the organization about which you inquired. In addition,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "the jurisdiction and responsibilities of the FBI, strictly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "an investigative agency of the Federal Government, do not",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "extend to furnishing evaluations or comments concerning",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "the character or integrity of any organization, publication",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "or individual. I am sure you will understand the necessity",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "for this policy and will not infer that we do or do not",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "have in our files the information you desire.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "In view of your interest in the internal",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "security of the United States, I am enclosing some",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "literature which you may wish to read.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
